  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An apocalypse that won't stop escalating.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zone B Korosu is a narrative-driven action epic where characters, perspectives, and gameplay evolve alongside the story. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hold onto your shotgun shells and expect things to go from 'normal day at work' to 'will we survive the night?' </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mix of fast-paced action sequences and down-tempo chillzones</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple character perspectives across the campaign</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evolving playstyles; one continuous story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >World of NPCs to interact with...or not!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro-inspired pixel art style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Digestible playtime (2-4 hrs)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High-energy soundtrack</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An apocalypse that won't stop escalating.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zone B Korosu is a narrative-driven action epic where characters, perspectives, and gameplay evolve alongside the story. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hold onto your shotgun shells and expect things to go from 'normal day at work' to 'will we survive the night?' </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mix of fast-paced action sequences and down-tempo chillzones</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple character perspectives across the campaign</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evolving playstyles; one continuous story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >World of NPCs to interact with...or not!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro-inspired pixel art style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Digestible playtime (2-4 hrs)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High-energy soundtrack</p></li></ul>",
